{
  "stem": "26765.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I said, you know, sister, I said, it's hard for me to believe that some of the extraordinary doctrines that the Catholic religion expects a person to believe, like the Immaculate Conception and the miracles and so on.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And she said, oh, everybody has doubts.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Don't worry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That will fall into place.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But I started, again, my search and that search lasted for a long time because I was confused about who I was and my identity, where I belonged.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And finally when I was about 40 years old, I found my way back to Judaism, and I took the name back of Levy.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "In the meantime, I married, and I have two children for whom I wrote my memoirs and for whom I'm giving this oral testimony to.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But it sent me definitely on an odyssey, a search for myself, for my identity, for my roots, for my religion.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I always loved school.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was the place where I felt secure and I felt I knew what I had to do.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I studied a lot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so the teachers thought I was OK, and that was in Holland as well as here.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I had a very good education at the Immaculata High School with the nuns.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I had four years of English, four years of math, four years of science.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I worked during my high school years.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I worked as a babysitter every Saturday evening, and I worked also as a nurse's aid in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Now, I wasn't too keen about going into nursing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I wanted to be a teacher, but my uncle, he thought every girl should be a nurse.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And so he wanted me to be a nurse.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I did go into nursing.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
